 Camoji is one of the first apps to take advantage of Facebook 's decision to open up Messenger , revealed at f8 conference in San Francisco .
Camoji allows people to add Instagram style filters to their images before sharing them .
The GIFs are created in the Camoji app .
They can add filters and other effects - similar to Instagram .
The world 's biggest social network has opened their Messenger app to seamless integration with third parties .